  "title": "HR Business Partner #ESY",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>•\tResponsible for payroll & CPF contributions for all employees under Singapore / Malaysia employment.</p><p>•\tAdvertising and sourcing of available positions.</p><p>•\tArranging interviews, screening, and trainings where necessary.</p><p>•\tEnsuring all government regulations regarding foreign hires are followed.</p><p>•\tGuiding Workers through onboarding orientations and exit interviews.</p><p>•\tEnsuring new hires are in the Facial Recognition System.</p><p></p><p>Internship Management</p><p>•\tLiaise with local institutions to source and recruit interns</p><p>•\tCoordinate intern interviews, screening, onboarding, and required training programs</p><p>•\tEnsure full compliance with government regulations and legal requirements for foreign interns and hires</p><p>•\tOversee and guide interns throughout the internship program</p><p>•\tPrepare and compile HR and other ad-hoc reports.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p>",
